%% Diagram: CSSOM vs DOM construction timeline
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Net as Network
    participant HP as HTML parser
    participant CP as CSS parser
    participant R as Renderer (style recalc + paint)

    Net-->>HP: HTML chunk 1
    HP-->>R: Partial DOM exposed (incremental)
    Net-->>CP: CSS bytes (chunk 1)
    Note over CP: Buffered; partial CSSOM not exposed
    Net-->>HP: HTML chunk 2
    HP-->>R: More DOM nodes (still incremental)
    Net-->>CP: CSS bytes (last chunk)
    CP->>CP: Tokenize, parse, build CSSOM
    CP-->>R: CSSOM ready (atomic)
    Note over R: Style recalc + First Contentful Paint may proceed
